{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756", "id": 511797241, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU1MTE3OTcyNDE=", "number": 65756, "title": "Do not derive Clone/Copy/etc for opaque types", "user": {"login": "VeaaC", "id": 14972638, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE0OTcyNjM4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/14972638?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC", "html_url": "https://github.com/VeaaC", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/VeaaC/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2019-10-24T08:44:12Z", "updated_at": "2019-10-24T14:50:56Z", "closed_at": "2019-10-24T09:24:14Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Currently bindgen will generate code that derives for opaque types, e.g.:\r\n\r\n``` C\r\ntypedef struct MyOpaqueStruct MyOpaqueStruct;\r\n```\r\n\r\n``` rust\r\n#[derive(Copy, Clone, Debug)]\r\npub struct MyOpaqueStruct {\r\n    _unused: [u8; 0],\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis has several problems:\r\n* If a user can obtain a reference to a type they can clone it, even though that is normally only possible through FFI calls, and will almost always result in UB\r\n* It prevents a user from implementing those traits on their own\r\n\r\nThe only current solution seems to be to turn of those derivations completely, forcing a user to implement them manually on the non-opaque types.\r\n\r\nI would suggest to just not derive any of these in case of an opaque struct (since I cannot come up with a use-case were they would actually work)", "closed_by": {"login": "jonas-schievink", "id": 1786438, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3ODY0Mzg=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1786438?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink", "html_url": "https://github.com/jonas-schievink", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65756/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_